      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Open race - none of them would truly shock. Leaning to SHOOTER MCGAVIN (2) who has finished second in all four of his synthetic track runs, giving a bold sight up on speed here in a similar race last time out when only run down by a long neck. Gets every hope from the soft draw and there doesn't look much pressure so he can go one better. MISS MAHJONG (4) struggled in a much stronger race at Caulfield Heath last time but had been coming along nicely prior and boasts an imposing record at this track which is key. She'll be very hard to hold out.  MALE MODEL (3) was good last time in town when working into third behind Ultra Blue who goes around earlier as favourite. He struggled his only go synthetic but can figure here. ALZARO (7) hasn't won in a while but is going okay and should be running on.",
